            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Characterization of Experimental Oro-Nasal Inoculation of Seba’s Short-Tailed Bats (Carollia perspicillata) with Bat Influenza A Virus H18N11",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
